TO USE A NEW RASPBERRY PI!

Install OpenCV3

Update your raspberri pi
sudo apt-get update
sudo apt-get dist-upgrade
sudo rpi-update
reboot


Add development tools for raspbian
sudo apt-get install build-essential

install compiler (4.9 the highest. Dont get 5.x or above)
sudo apt-get install gcc


Download dlib-master.zip. Recompile
https://github.com/davisking/dlib

compile by moving into example folder 
mkdir build; cd build; cmake ..; cmake --build .
